{"tid":1465933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"要整一部抗爭憲法","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:25:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T00:57:39.000Z","uid":261635,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a3d72030da6f79ced425c402da66978b7155c845","tid":1465933,"uid":261635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:25:38.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都見到有唔少鬼帶風向或者帶頭打firstaid同記者，同埋又係到辱罵遊客，呢啲都係極傷害成個抗爭形象嘅行為。<br />\n<br />\n為咗令啲鬼無得再傷害運動嘅形象，我提議訂立一部抗爭憲法，set定一啲唔可以做嘅嘢，令每一位手足都知道應該底線係邊，咁先至唔會令到班狗同港共有位攻擊我哋。<br />\n<br />\n我先提幾條應該無乜人會反對嘅先<br />\n1. 不割蓆，不分化，不放棄（當然唔代表唔可以提出建議）<br />\n2. 謹記抗爭目標，勿忘初衷（避免運動失去方向）<br />\n3. 尊重同協助救護同記者工作（戰爭基本原則）<br />\n4. 不傷害無辜（警狗除外）<br />\n5. 不為個人私利（防止出現搶掠）<br />\n6. 以和善理性嘅態度與他人溝通（啲遊客見到成班人圍住佢嚟鬧好傷形象）<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家提出意見，當呢部憲法成型嘅時候，就永遠都唔會有大台出現，因為每個人都會係大台。"},{"pid":"212962417b85034484b8302e21f9f80b30850c2e","tid":1465933,"uid":165515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:28:27.000Z","msg":"認同！"},{"pid":"be12850e26a68bbee2a83c2b06aa41ea218b9861","tid":1465933,"uid":165515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:31:35.000Z","msg":"811"},{"pid":"973a84c7acf3bec2b17091d4151e17a0d2d89582","tid":1465933,"uid":165515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:31:46.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"844cfae7b306c89ce202345631212e17e6bc9132","tid":1465933,"uid":165515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:31:56.000Z","msg":"69"},{"pid":"ae6cde41c99ab197e8d8039f936bedc0fa7217c4","tid":1465933,"uid":165515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"612"},{"pid":"05ec2c10e0f77b8355efee9c634801a65cc7ea88","tid":1465933,"uid":261635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:36:08.000Z","msg":"連登仔個個iq200，幫手一齊度下橋"},{"pid":"855011849a0e504b6fdb7947bcccfc58385a7c07","tid":1465933,"uid":18296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:36:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86c9b11bc855f256de01128c8238d09c5d366e3e","tid":1465933,"uid":261635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:42:53.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"1ab6f33462ea4865aa67ed4f207305f8c73b8f7c","tid":1465933,"uid":261635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:00.000Z","msg":"唔好沉啊！"},{"pid":"eb5f98f926fd1c0edbaa457f4e28b575f277e966","tid":1465933,"uid":29962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:13:15.000Z","msg":"69"},{"pid":"58c75c69a4036637e9e7586a4d861001b0572710","tid":1465933,"uid":261635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T00:57:39.000Z","msg":"612"}]}